        <title xml:id="spp-132-06H1-title-1">THE<lb/>  VIRTUES OF SID HAMET<lb/>  THE<lb/>  MAGICIAN's ROD <ref target="#spp-132-06H1-footnote-title-1">1</ref><note n="1" xml:id="spp-132-06H1-footnote-title-1" place="foot">The staff of lord treasurer <hi rend="italics">Godolphin</hi>, which, on the 29th of <hi rend="italics">May</hi> 1711, was given to <hi rend="italics">Robert Harley</hi>, earl of <hi rend="italics">Oxford</hi></note>.</title>
